<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.7.9">
<l>īṭum valiyu muṭaiya vinnam pipiṟan taveḻu tiṅkaḷil</l>
<l>ēṭalar kaṇṇiyi ṉāṉai vaḷartti yamuṉainī rāṭap pōṉēṉ</l>
<l>cēṭaṉ tirumaṟu mārvaṉ kiṭantu tiruvaṭiyāl malai pōla</l>
<l>vōṭum cakaṭattaic cāṭiya piṉṉai yurappuva tañcu vēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In the seventh month since this prince with [such] size and strength was born,</l>
<l>Laying down that one who has a garland of petalled flowers,</l>
<l rend="indent">I went to the Yamunā [River] to bath;</l>
<l>After the child, the one with the divine mark on his chest, laying there,</l>
<l>Toppled a mountain-like rolling cart with his divine feet,</l>
<l rend="indent">I am afraid of being firm.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
